          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05045">To ask the Secretary of State for Education and Skills if he will allow local education authorities to renegotiate their targets for key stage two. [134324]</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_82ws' title='Col. 82WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c82WS' name='column_82ws' href='#column_82ws' rel='bookmark'>82WS</a><p id="S6CV0412P0-05046"><table>
